{"tid":1844382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"彩瑛@TWICE手機號碼外洩遭轟炸　發文籲自律","createTime":"2020-01-26T15:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T03:53:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"853da337ff39ab8b298d6e7c0826479b7d413405","tid":1844382,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:08:43.000Z","msg":"韓團TWICE的20歲成員彩瑛今日在Instagram發文透露因手機號碼在網上外洩而造成困擾：「因為某些人的不體諒與不尊重，將沒有任何意思的11個數字在網上公開那瞬間起，我的手機便被大批來電與短訊轟炸。」她續說：「只是想表達關心和愛，卻在沒有任何考慮下作出的行動與聯絡，對這麼多人造成疲勞與不安，拜託，請稍為考慮一吓吧！」呼籲狂迷自律，別再為她添麻煩！"},{"pid":"57e428a627a99fa26159c4de15df939fe9090e53","tid":1844382,"uid":132174,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"幫佢訂外買"},{"pid":"4848f00b2a8c821ce38308cfd0d3135b1dfca4e2","tid":1844382,"uid":43061,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:13:29.000Z","msg":"賺左啦 透明人都有得上報"},{"pid":"9322885f304897463846cf58f44b187ec91ad04a","tid":1844382,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/da5da3c0975f88448b634a8115432e65/124faf0a4d4caf07-f2/s400x600/a25c3b300c529c23d1cea3f061bb5114e446fc98.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fda5da3c0975f88448b634a8115432e65%2F124faf0a4d4caf07-f2%2Fs400x600%2Fa25c3b300c529c23d1cea3f061bb5114e446fc98.gif&h=afdc2d2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又鄙視我地once<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba36aabf54b538731570a75378922b3377c7ddf","tid":1844382,"uid":294121,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"成隊唯一一個有佢電話都唔會想打俾佢既成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d746b0d7c31161e58cd890592c985a4c3d1b5f","tid":1844382,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ba36aabf54b538731570a75378922b3377c7ddf","tid":1844382,"uid":294121,"like":18,"dislike":4,"s